text: Young's Motorsports is an American professional stock car racing team that competes in the NASCAR Xfinity Series, NASCAR Craftsman Truck Series, and the ARCA Menards Series. On January 3, 2024, it was announced that the team would start racing in the NASCAR Xfinity Series in 2024. That same day, Leland Honeyman was announced as the full-time driver of the No. 42 car. On January 14, 2025, it was announced that Anthony Alfredo would drive the No. 42 car full time. ==References== Category:Auto racing
